library(tidyverse)
readdata <- read_csv("D://Stat210/rainfall.csv")
raindata <- data.frame(readdata)
seed <- raindata[raindata[,1]==1,2]
noseed <- raindata[raindata[,1]==0,2]
describe(seed)
describe(noseed)
hist(seed)
hist(noseed)
qqnorm(seed)
qqnorm(noseed)
logseed <- log(seed)
lognoseed <- log(noseed)
describe(logseed)
describe(lognoseed)
hist(logseed)
hist(lognoseed)
qqnorm(logseed)
qqnorm(lognoseed)
t.test(seed,noseed)
t.test(logseed,lognoseed)
